					<p class="landing-p">Sense-It is a community art project for the residents of Punggol.</p>
					<p class="landing-p">Sense-It participants will assemble hobby sensor kits and collect environmental data from this neighbourhood.</p>
					<p class="landing-p">Data such as air-particulate matter levels, sound levels, and UV levels would give us an opportunity to appreciate the relationships we cultivate from living in Punggol.</p>
