				<div class="landing-participant-text">My favorite activity in Punggol is line-dancing at Oasis Terraces every Tuesday night. My friends and I would bring kueh-kueh and cakes. We would chit chat and have kopi after our dance session. </div>
			</div>
		</div>

<!-- end of 3rd row -->
</div>



